update config from the environment
    mode


update config from the command line
    address
    command (restart, runfg, start, status, stop)
    mode
    root


look for <root>/aspen.conf or <root>/etc/aspen.conf
    having both is an error
if etc/aspen.conf, then look for extras for sys.path
    lib/python
    lib/python{x.y}
    lib/plat-...


update config from aspen.conf
    address
    defaults
    http_version
    mode
    threads


load middleware from middleware key in default section of aspen.conf
    middleware = aspen.middleware:foo
                 aspen.middleware:bar
                 aspen.middleware:baz
load apps from [apps] section in aspen.conf
    / = aspen.apps:static
